OL,5,G0305 Noel Edmonds' Kiwi Adventure
OL,6,     FAfter 50 years in the spotlight,
OL,7,     FNoel Edmonds left his TV career
OL,8,     Fbehind and started a new life in
OL,9,     FNew Zealand with his wife Liz in
OL,10,     F2018. They bought land in the
OL,11,     Fquiet town of Ngatimoti, where
OL,12,     Fthey have been building a
OL,13,     Fhospitality business. This series
OL,14,     Ffollows the couple's journey as
OL,15,     Fthey battle the challenges of
OL,16,     Fsmall-town life and try to turn
OL,17,     Ftheir vision into a success while
OL,18,     Fnavigating the pressure of being
OL,19,     Fseen as outsiders
